metadata.description:
This charming design is a tired but energetic snake, if you own this charming snake, you will enter our club and you will also receive unique points.
Login to our game to earn money, get free nft for next collections and many other features are among the benefits of buying these nfts.
If you want to know more about the club and our future plans, please check out the project website and read its roadmap.
metadata.name: Bored Snake #1 V2
